&lt;li&gt;Own end-to-end calendar management for the CEO, prioritizing time against company goals, stakeholder needs, and leadership cadences; proactively resolve conflicts and protect prep, travel, and deep-work windows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with the Chief of Staff, Head of Office of the CEO, and other EAs to ensure the CEO’s schedule reflects strategic priorities and that handoffs are seamless.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan and manage detailed domestic and international travel, including itineraries, and logistics for board meetings, off-sites, and external appearances.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build lightweight systems and documentation that improve executive workflows; use modern productivity tools and AI to increase speed, quality, and reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a high-judgment point of contact for internal and external stakeholders, maintaining confidentiality and representing the CEO’s office with professionalism.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;✅&amp;nbsp; You have...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Significant experience supporting a CEO, founder, or senior executive with complex, fast-changing schedules and priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated excellence in high-volume calendar orchestration, logistics, and meeting readiness, with a track record of anticipating needs and solving problems proactively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outstanding organization and written/verbal communication skills; you keep details tight, documentation clear, and stakeholders aligned.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unshakeable discretion and judgment; calm, focused execution under pressure; and a service mindset that helps leaders operate at their best.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort collaborating across senior leadership and cross-functional teams, and working in person with the Office of the CEO and other EAs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with modern productivity and collaboration tools (G Suite, Slack, Zoom, Mac) and an interest in leveraging AI to streamline workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;⭐&amp;nbsp; Exceptional candidates will have...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years supporting CEOs in high-growth or complex organizations.&lt;/li&gt;
