&lt;li&gt;Collaborate deeply with product teams to increase in-app shareability, surface community-driven content, and create in-app features that reward and incentivize organic advocacy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build the attribution and measurement infrastructure that connects community and creator activity to business outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure new feature launches, vertical expansions, and cultural moments are systematically amplified through creator and community channels&lt;/li&gt;
