&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Over the last few years, Duolingo has expanded beyond language learning into entirely new subjects: Math, Music, and Chess. These products reach millions of daily active users, are growing quickly, and represent a CEO-level bet that Duolingo can become a platform for learning anything.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a Senior Director of Engineering to co- lead our newest subjects, responsible for building and scaling products ranging from early stages through to some of the company’s fastest-growing initiatives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a role for a builder. You&#39;ll make decisions about which subjects to invest in, how to allocate engineering resources across bets at different stages, where to continue investing and where to pivot.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll partner closely with Product and Design to shape the future of the pillar while building the organization that delivers it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is based in our New York, NY office on a hybrid (4+1) work schedule.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🧠&amp;nbsp; You will...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive the product and technical strategy across &lt;strong&gt;Music and Chess&lt;/strong&gt;, balancing short-term product impact with long-term strategic goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner strategically with &lt;strong&gt;Product, Design, Learning and AI&lt;/strong&gt; to evolve our strategy, including decisions on when and how to expand to additional subjects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead multiple engineering directors and their teams as they tackle some of the most interesting technical challenges in industry: AI-based content creation at scale, neural bots, and Unity-based gameplay.&lt;/li&gt;
